author: @andyle5716
text:
Finally ep 7 is uploaded. Does anyone know the reason why it wasn't uploaded last Friday? It first starts off with Yujinie the driver, who recently got her driver licence. She's driving nicely and responsibly. And they've arrived safely to the destination. Maknae is so funny, saying Yujinie's the best driver. She's the only driver. And Wony's 'phew' at the end. 
This week's episode of 1, 2, 3 IVE was so hilarious to watch. Their variety shows are getting more chaotic, but that's what I love about IVE. Neomu usgyeo. 😂 The Kitsch game was hilarious to watch. IVE are split up into teams. Sentimentals vs YoungLiz in the cooking showdown. And they're cooking with a variety of Ramyun. Sentimentals' Ramyun fried rice looking delicious. And YoungLiz's Chapaghetti with Dongpo pork looks delicious too. Now I'm hungry. And LiMakz are the hilariously funny food critics. And YoungLiz come out on top. Let's go! I'm sure Sentimentals Ramyun fried rice was good too, but I agree with Maknae. Too much onion. I'm looking forward to watching next week's episode.
